text: Niamh played for Durham University Women's football from 2023 to 2024
Niamh played for Doncaster Rovers Belles first team from 2021 to 2022
Niamh played for Sheffield United U21s from 2020 to 2021. She made her first team debut at 16
Niamh played for Sheffield United Academy from 2019 to 2020.
